payload.content:
Thought: 项目中已找到 flybird_game 目录，且其 styles.css 文件是负责界面样式的主文件。当前样式较为简洁、非卡通风格，需优化为更卡通、更生动的视觉效果。我将修改 styles.css 来增强 UI 的卡通感，包括使用更鲜艳的颜色、圆角设计、添加阴影和动画效果等。
Action: file_writer[{"path": "flybird_game/styles.css", "content": "body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
    background-color: #ffebc6; /* 柔和的奶油色背景 */
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
}

#game-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 400px;
    height: 600px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid #ff69b4; /* 粉色边框，增加卡通感 */
    border-radius: 20px;
    background-color: #a8e6cf; /* 轻盈的绿色背景，类似草地 */
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* 添加柔和阴影 */
}

#game-canvas {
    display: block;
}

#ui {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15px;
    left: 15px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    border: 2px dashed #ff69b4;
}

button {
    padding: 12px 18px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    background-color: #ff69b4;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 25px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.3);
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #ff50a4;
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(255, 105, 180, 0.5);
}

button:active {
    transform: scale(0.95);
}

#score, #history {
    font-size: 18px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 2px solid #ff69b4;
    box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    text-align: center;
}

/* 卡通风格装饰元素 */
#ui::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: -10px;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    background-color: #ff69b4;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff69b4;
    opacity: 0.5;
}

#ui::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    right: -10px;
    width: 25px;
    height: 25px;
    background-color: #a8e6cf;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #a8e6cf;
    opacity: 0.5;
}"}]

